 "Create the case story. A good case is one \nthat describes a controversy or sets the scene by describing the characters \ninvolved and the situation. It should also allow for some action to be taken \nin order to gain resolution of the situation.": "Vytvo\u0159it p\u0159\u00edpadovou studii.\nDobr\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edkladem je zachycen\u00ed kontroverzn\u00ed situace \nnebo sc\u00e9ny popisem chov\u00e1n\u00ed zainteresovan\u00fdch osob. M\u011bla by se tak\u00e9 vz\u00edt v \u00favahu \nmo\u017enost reakce, kter\u00e1 napom\u016f\u017ee vy\u0159e\u0161en\u00ed situace.", 
