 "Type the learning objectives for this resource.": "Vepi\u0161te v\u00fdukov\u00e9 c\u00edle tohoto prost\u0159edku.", 
 "Teachers should keep the following in mind when using this iDevice: <ol><li>Think about the number of different types of activity planned for your resource that will be visually signalled in the content. Avoid using too many different types or classification of activities otherwise learner may become confused. Usually three or four different types are more than adequate for a teaching resource.<\/li><li>From a visual design perspective, avoid having two iDevices immediately following each other without any text in between. If this is required, rather collapse two questions or events into one iDevice. <\/li><li>Think about activities where the perceived benefit of doing the activity outweighs the time and effort it will take to complete the activity. <\/li><\/ol>": "U\u010ditel\u00e9 by p\u0159i pou\u017eit\u00ed tohoto iDevice m\u011bli br\u00e1t v potaz: <ol><li> P\u0159em\u00fd\u0161lejte nad mno\u017estv\u00edm r\u016fzn\u00fdch zam\u00fd\u0161len\u00fdch aktivit, kter\u00e9 budou v obsahu vizu\u00e1ln\u011b ozna\u010deny. Vyhn\u011bte se p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 velk\u00e9mu mno\u017estv\u00ed r\u016fzn\u00fdch typ\u016f \u010di klasifikac\u00ed aktivit, proto\u017ee to m\u016f\u017ee v\u00e9st ke zmaten\u00ed student\u016f. Obvykle sta\u010d\u00ed t\u0159i a\u017e \u010dty\u0159i r\u016fzn\u00e9 typy na jednu v\u00fdukovou jednotku.<\/li><li> Pro p\u0159ehlednost se v\u017edy sna\u017ete vkl\u00e1dat mezi dv\u011b iDevice text. Pokud to ale nejde, rad\u011bji shr\u0148te dv\u011b ot\u00e1zky \u010di p\u0159\u00edpady do jednoho iDevice.<\/li><li> Berte do \u00favahy aktivity, u kter\u00fdch p\u0159edpokl\u00e1dan\u00fd efekt p\u0159ev\u00e1\u017e\u00ed nad \u010dasem a \u00fasil\u00edm, kter\u00e9 jsou nutn\u00e9 k jejich dokon\u010den\u00ed.<\/li><\/ol>", 
