 "Spanish Wikipedia Article": "\u010cl\u00e1nek ve Wikipedii \u0161pan\u011blsky", 
 "A case study is a device that provides learners \nwith a simulation that has an educational basis. It takes a situation, generally \nbased in reality, and asks learners to demonstrate or describe what action they \nwould take to complete a task or resolve a situation. The case study allows \nlearners apply their own knowledge and experience to completing the tasks \nassigned. when designing a case study consider the following:<ul> \n<li>\tWhat educational points are conveyed in the story<\/li>\n<li>\tWhat preparation will the learners need to do prior to working on the \ncase study<\/li>\n<li>\tWhere the case study fits into the rest of the course<\/li>\n<li>\tHow the learners will interact with the materials and each other e.g.\nif run in a classroom situation can teams be setup to work on different aspects\nof the case and if so how are ideas feed back to the class<\/li><\/ul>": "P\u0159\u00edpadov\u00e1 studie je iDevice, kter\u00fd se vzd\u011bl\u00e1vac\u00edm z\u00e1m\u011brem simuluje re\u00e1lnou situaci. Jsou jimi zpravidla \nre\u00e1ln\u00e9 situace, u kter\u00fdch jsou studenti vyzv\u00e1ni k p\u0159edveden\u00ed \u010di popisu jedn\u00e1n\u00ed,\n je\u017e m\u016f\u017ee v\u00e9st k vy\u0159e\u0161en\u00ed dan\u00e9 situace. P\u0159\u00edpadov\u00e1 studie umo\u017e\u0148uje \n student\u016fm pou\u017e\u00edt sv\u00e9 vlastn\u00ed znalosti a zku\u0161enosti k vy\u0159e\u0161en\u00ed uveden\u00fdch \u00fakol\u016f. Kdy\u017e vytv\u00e1\u0159\u00edte p\u0159\u00edpadovou studii, berte na v\u011bdom\u00ed n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00ed:<ul> \n<li> Jak\u00e9 vzd\u011bl\u00e1vac\u00ed aspekty jsou p\u0159\u00edb\u011bhem zprost\u0159edkov\u00e1ny.<\/li>\n<li> Jakou p\u0159\u00edpravu budou studenti pot\u0159ebovat pro pr\u00e1ci na p\u0159\u00edpadov\u00e9 studii.<\/li>\n<li> Jak p\u0159\u00edpadov\u00e1 studie zapad\u00e1 do zbytku kurzu. <\/li>\n <li> Jak budou studenti vyu\u017e\u00edvat materi\u00e1ly a vz\u00e1jemn\u011b spolupracovat, nap\u0159.\n kdy\u017e situace ve t\u0159\u00edd\u011b umo\u017en\u00ed vytvo\u0159en\u00ed t\u00fdm\u016f pracuj\u00edc\u00edch na r\u016fzn\u00fdch aspektech p\u0159\u00edpadu a jakou zp\u011btnou vazbu z toho t\u0159\u00edda z\u00edsk\u00e1.<\/li><\/ul>", 
